Marry, sir, the letter, very orderly;


having nothing but the word 'noddy' for my

pains.

I have loved her ever since I saw
her;
and still I see her beautiful.

Out with that too;
it was Eve's
legacy, and cannot be ta'en from her.

Master, be one of them;
it's an honorable
kind of thievery.
